user.nickname: 三宝徒步西藏（黑龙江大庆）
user.signature:
2020年3🈷️31号
黑龙江省大庆市出发徒步西藏阿里冈仁波齐,全程7000公里。
黑龙江省➡️吉林省➡️内蒙古自治区➡️河北省➡️北京市➡️山西省➡️陕西省➡️四川省➡️西藏拉萨➡️（阿里冈仁波齐）磕大头绕山（三圈共165公里）
生活就像一场徒步旅行,穿越荆棘和沼泽,我们终将会迎来最美的风景。
⚠️只要走路，全程直播！

{"cid":"1572072504832002","cha_name":"王一博","desc":"王一博，中国内地男歌手、演员、职业摩托车赛车手，1997年8月5日出生于河南洛阳。2014年9月15日，作为UNIQ组合成员出道，2016年4月加入《天天向上》。第30届中国电视金鹰奖观众喜爱的男演员。《陪你到世界之巅》饰季向空，《陈情令》饰蓝忘机，《有翡》饰谢允，《冰雨火》饰陈宇，《风起洛阳》饰百里弘毅。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1572072504832002","author":{"uid":"101562100101","short_id":"2014940272","nickname":"王一博吧_WYBBar","gender":1,"signature":"王一博是最酷的盖","avatar_larger":{"uri":"tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f","url_list":["https://p9.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=4010531038","https://p6.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=4010531038","https://p3.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=4010531038"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f","url_list":["https://p26.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=4010531038","https://p9.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=4010531038","https://p6.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=4010531038"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f","url_list":["https://p6.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=4010531038","https://p3.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=4010531038","https://p9.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=4010531038"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":
